    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――芽衣と怜による期間限定ユニットのライブ当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "それで、この間寮で怜ちゃんを呼んでも\n全然返事がなくて～",
      "startTime": 6.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "部屋に入ったらぐっっっすり寝てるの！",
      "startTime": 8.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "それで耳をこしょこしょ～ってしたらね？\nすっごい気持ち良さそうに……あ、やば",
      "startTime": 16.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ごめん、ごめんってば！\nこれ以上は言わない、言わないよー！",
      "startTime": 25.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4011.0429446,
          "startTime": 27.0110429446
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、怜ちゃんに怒られる前に\n次の曲行っちゃおー！",
      "startTime": 33.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3800.000000000001,
          "startTime": 34.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（怜の父親が会場に来るかどうかが気になって）\n（ライブの初めは、二人とも浮き足立っていたけど）",
      "startTime": 40.3433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（まずい……と思ったその時、なんと怜の父親が会場に）\n（現れたのだ。そこから二人は一気に調子を取り戻し）",
      "startTime": 48.7433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（終盤では、お披露目ライブとは思えないほど）\n（堂々としたパフォーマンスを見せてくれた）",
      "startTime": 57.32,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー！　今日は来てくれて本当にありがとー！",
      "startTime": 60.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "私達と、もちろんサニピ、月ストもよろしくねー！",
      "startTime": 68.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.666666600011,
          "startTime": 72.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、お父さん来てくれて良かったね",
      "startTime": 75.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、大好きな怜ちゃんと踊れて最高の気分だよ\nぜーったいまた一緒にやろうね！",
      "startTime": 85.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（いろいろあったけど、結局二人のライブは）\n（大成功に終わったな……）",
      "startTime": 92.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "はー、今日は楽しかったー！",
      "startTime": 96,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。凄くいいライブだったな",
      "startTime": 101.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～\n{user}さん、ありがとー！",
      "startTime": 106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "最初はどうなることかと思ったけど\n無事に終わってよかったー",
      "startTime": 112.3433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "それに……怜ちゃんのお父さんも観に来てくれたしね",
      "startTime": 114.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんが来てからの怜ちゃん、凄かった",
      "startTime": 120.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスもキレキレだし、表情もキラキラしてて……\n芽衣も負けるもんかーって頑張れたんだよね",
      "startTime": 128.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに二人とも、歌もダンスもキレがあったよ",
      "startTime": 133.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "それにね？\n怜ちゃん、ライブの後はとっても優しい顔してたんだ",
      "startTime": 139.21,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "こんな顔するんだーってびっくりしちゃった\nすっごく可愛かったんだよ？",
      "startTime": 147.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。俺も見てみたかったな",
      "startTime": 149.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、まさか怜のご実家に突撃するとはな……\nまったく、あんまり無茶はするなよ？",
      "startTime": 159.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさーい\nみんなにも叱られたんだよね",
      "startTime": 166.31,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "特に沙季ちゃんが……はわわわわ",
      "startTime": 169.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "反省してるならいいんだ……今回は、芽衣が怜のことを\n真剣に想って行動したから、状況が変わった訳だしな",
      "startTime": 180.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣のおかげで今回のライブは成功したし\n怜も成長出来たんだと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 187.79,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なのかな\nそうだといいな、えへへ",
      "startTime": 193.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "なんだろ、怜ちゃんが褒められると\n芽衣まで嬉しくなるなー",
      "startTime": 200.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は……本当に優しいな",
      "startTime": 202.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei022.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの当たり前じゃーん！\n怜ちゃんは大事な仲間なんだからね！",
      "startTime": 209.12,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei023.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 212.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_03-mei024.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、怜ちゃんとのユニット\nいつもの月ストとは違った楽しさがあったの！",
      "startTime": 217.54,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
